{"id": 1045, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在什么事情上耐心会特别少？ ", "description": "与其和你在这儿耗，我宁愿去玩水果忍者。（题目来自：Sam Chivers）", "record_count": 5967, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181408xN4qeEzbvymoQuW6.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-23T11:00:03Z", "options": [{"id": 91904, "content": "做细节活上，大概有十分钟热度，嘻嘻", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654863}, {"id": 92160, "content": "等待   比如等车 ，等人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92714}, {"id": 91905, "content": "网页打不开", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643161}, {"id": 92161, "content": "洗澡…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533866}, {"id": 93697, "content": "不管宅在家有多无聊，就是能在床上躺一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660766}, {"id": 91906, "content": "和不喜欢的人聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643161}, {"id": 91907, "content": "对不喜欢不在乎的人聊聊天、刷朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654875}, {"id": 91908, "content": "做作业   尤其是难的作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654866}, {"id": 91909, "content": "懒得打字、语音多好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654875}, {"id": 97797, "content": "等人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152720}, {"id": 91910, "content": "期末复习", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635745}, {"id": 91911, "content": "对待家人的情绪上，事后每每反思，但痛苦始终不能让人警醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654883}, {"id": 91912, "content": "网上申请爱存不存银行的换个球旅行信用卡禁卡。多达几十项内容填写接近尾声时…一言不合网页就卡顿出翔来…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 92168, "content": "人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650110}, {"id": 91913, "content": "等", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635729}, {"id": 91914, "content": "等车，尤其是在等公交的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610307}, {"id": 91915, "content": "重复性的任何事情????", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577698}, {"id": 91916, "content": "三观不同还需要沟通，啊，头好痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639568}, {"id": 91917, "content": "和脑电波不在一个频率上的人聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645814}, {"id": 92173, "content": "嘿咻的时候还要脱丝袜，真麻烦，直接撕了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270109}, {"id": 104205, "content": "网卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 91918, "content": "看书！一点耐心都没！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 92430, "content": "微信有99+的留言，每条语音一两秒左右", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656244}, {"id": 91919, "content": "打架", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463935}, {"id": 93711, "content": "等加载，手机加载，电脑加载，还半天加不出来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 510947}, {"id": 91920, "content": "开会=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487739}, {"id": 91921, "content": "球赛开始半小时都没有进球就关视频了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646888}, {"id": 91922, "content": "打撸啊撸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634663}, {"id": 91923, "content": "等车", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612295}, {"id": 97043, "content": "慢哟哟地走在我前面，而且还是因为在玩儿手机。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258474}, {"id": 91925, "content": "看的视频总长1分钟，广告就30秒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654926}, {"id": 92693, "content": "从零开始一段新的感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657007}, {"id": 93461, "content": "做不感兴趣的事的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659403}, {"id": 91926, "content": "谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231295}, {"id": 92182, "content": "和沟通有障碍的人沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655527}, {"id": 91927, "content": "缓冲", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463609}, {"id": 91928, "content": "十秒内不来验证码", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463609}, {"id": 91929, "content": "等待啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601008}, {"id": 91930, "content": "太长不看", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642472}, {"id": 91932, "content": "字好快呀，都看不清", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654936}, {"id": 91933, "content": "家里人看点四十吵死了，烦烦烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654936}, {"id": 91934, "content": "帮别人拎包等她试衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654939}, {"id": 91935, "content": "这样都是干嘛的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654936}, {"id": 99615, "content": "永远都觉得自己对别人错的聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683498}, {"id": 91936, "content": "不知道说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654936}, {"id": 98336, "content": "听逻辑混乱的人叙述事情经过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 91937, "content": "找个工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566983}, {"id"